WEBVTT

01:39.370 --> 01:43.640
[Road to Success]

01:44.670 --> 01:47.850
[Episode 10]

02:26.960 --> 02:27.750
Is he asleep?

02:29.030 --> 02:29.800
Yes.

02:31.030 --> 02:32.430
Here is Xinshu's
household registration booklet.

02:32.430 --> 02:33.690
I'll leave it with you.

02:35.660 --> 02:38.840
[Head of Household: Guan Minjie]

02:44.030 --> 02:46.070
He's sleeping soundly now.

02:46.870 --> 02:48.400
Go check on him.

02:57.730 --> 02:58.610
Oh, Mom.

02:59.520 --> 03:00.310
Um...

03:00.910 --> 03:03.770
Wasn't there a death benefit
after Dad passed away?

03:03.910 --> 03:06.360
Something's come up recently,
and I need money.

03:06.360 --> 03:07.870
I want to borrow it for now.

03:09.310 --> 03:10.120
Mom.

03:10.240 --> 03:11.560
I have no say

03:12.240 --> 03:13.480
over that money.

03:14.310 --> 03:15.970
Your dad left it all to Xinshu.

03:16.710 --> 03:17.590
What?

03:19.800 --> 03:22.000
Before your dad passed away, he said

03:22.680 --> 03:23.800
you had a job

03:24.030 --> 03:25.800
and could support yourself,

03:26.180 --> 03:28.090
and that Xinshu was still young

03:28.150 --> 03:29.630
and would need a lot of money

03:29.630 --> 03:30.960
for school and everything else
in the future.

03:30.960 --> 03:32.030
-But...
-Besides,

03:32.960 --> 03:34.280
your dad left a will.

03:34.280 --> 03:36.000
But I really need the money.

03:36.000 --> 03:36.870
Mom.

03:43.400 --> 03:45.060
I don't mean to criticize you,

03:45.120 --> 03:48.850
but what kind of mother only gives birth
and never raises her child?

03:49.400 --> 03:50.310
Mom,

03:50.960 --> 03:53.030
it's not that I don't want to
take care of him.

03:53.030 --> 03:55.280
My husband told me to
make a clean break with Fu Haisheng,

03:55.280 --> 03:56.000
or he'd

03:56.590 --> 03:57.870
divorce me.

04:00.520 --> 04:02.320
I'll leave him in your care, Mom.

04:31.120 --> 04:35.050
[Mourning]

04:54.600 --> 04:55.390
Lin Wanxing!

04:56.510 --> 04:58.970
Fu Xinshu, what are you doing?
Are you crazy?

05:00.800 --> 05:01.730
Are you alright?

05:01.870 --> 05:02.720
Ms. Lin.

05:02.720 --> 05:04.510
Are you trying to get yourself killed?

05:04.510 --> 05:06.430
Ms. Lin, your hand!

05:07.500 --> 05:08.500
It's nothing.

05:19.010 --> 05:22.340
Turn right up ahead
and pick up the medicine at the pharmacy.

05:23.000 --> 05:24.120
How is Ms. Lin?

05:28.190 --> 05:29.270
She's fine.

05:30.070 --> 05:31.930
Just a few superficial injuries.

05:33.310 --> 05:34.159
I'm sorry.

05:35.390 --> 05:36.390
It's all my fault.

05:37.390 --> 05:38.240
I'm sorry.

05:43.040 --> 05:44.480
Fu Xinshu,

05:45.360 --> 05:46.870
there's nothing wrong

05:46.870 --> 05:47.600
with a person

05:47.600 --> 05:49.060
expressing anger or pain.

05:49.159 --> 05:51.620
But you went about it
the wrong way, you know?

05:53.620 --> 05:54.170
My...

05:56.260 --> 05:58.860
My mind just went completely blank
at the time.

05:59.150 --> 06:01.610
Running away from problems
is the stupidest

06:01.680 --> 06:03.280
and most useless thing to do.

06:07.690 --> 06:10.020
You think your problems
will just disappear

06:10.020 --> 06:11.090
if you run away?

06:12.920 --> 06:14.450
Let me tell you, they won't.

06:16.230 --> 06:19.360
You'll only end up
hurting the people who care about you.

06:21.800 --> 06:23.270
Next time, before you act on impulse,

06:23.270 --> 06:24.670
think about your family,

06:25.240 --> 06:26.600
think about your teammates,

06:26.600 --> 06:28.730
and think about your teacher, Ms. Lin.

06:34.560 --> 06:36.020
I won't do it again, Coach.

06:37.560 --> 06:38.360
I won't.

06:41.330 --> 06:42.300
I won't.

06:46.190 --> 06:47.630
Are you truly over it?

06:50.540 --> 06:51.950
Ms. Lin,

06:52.040 --> 06:53.190
I'm sorry.

06:54.870 --> 06:55.870
Fu Xinshu,

06:57.110 --> 06:59.060
have you really

07:00.600 --> 07:02.120
put this behind you?

07:08.380 --> 07:10.780
It doesn't matter whether I have or not.

07:27.240 --> 07:28.430
A wound

07:29.270 --> 07:31.930
has to be cleaned thoroughly
before it can heal,

07:32.560 --> 07:33.560
doesn't it?

07:34.600 --> 07:36.240
I just feel like

07:36.680 --> 07:39.070
nobody needs me.

07:43.750 --> 07:45.040
We need you.

07:47.000 --> 07:48.040
Fu Xinshu,

07:49.600 --> 07:51.000
we all need you.

07:57.870 --> 07:59.159
In my eyes,

08:01.800 --> 08:04.190
you're a very hardworking kid.

08:06.310 --> 08:07.560
You study hard

08:09.070 --> 08:10.240
and train hard.

08:12.240 --> 08:14.100
You're always the first to arrive

08:14.950 --> 08:16.270
at training

08:17.800 --> 08:19.000
and the last to leave.

08:21.000 --> 08:23.730
You quietly take care of everything
for the team.

08:26.110 --> 08:29.020
You've really helped me
more than you know.

08:33.030 --> 08:35.360
You're a very mature, good kid.

08:40.150 --> 08:41.600
What good is any of it?

08:44.240 --> 08:46.030
I know she doesn't like me.

08:47.510 --> 08:48.150
I...

08:50.600 --> 08:52.650
She only messages me

08:52.820 --> 08:54.660
and pretends to care

08:54.750 --> 08:56.550
when she wants money.

08:57.670 --> 08:58.550
But...

09:01.600 --> 09:03.320
I just didn't want to admit it.

09:03.320 --> 09:05.000
I didn't want to admit it.

09:09.360 --> 09:10.600
Ms. Lin...

09:16.230 --> 09:17.150
When I found out

09:17.150 --> 09:19.750
she wasn't sick, I was very happy.

09:19.750 --> 09:20.510
But...

09:23.240 --> 09:26.500
when I learned she'd given the money
to my younger brother,

09:27.150 --> 09:28.840
it really hurt.

09:42.360 --> 09:44.480
None of this is your fault.

09:48.080 --> 09:49.630
We are all born

09:52.000 --> 09:52.840
into circumstances

09:52.840 --> 09:54.840
we can't choose.

10:01.080 --> 10:02.880
If I could wish one thing for you,

10:05.750 --> 10:07.240
it's that you

10:09.600 --> 10:11.800
wouldn't always have to be so grown-up.

10:13.510 --> 10:14.910
You can cry if you want to.

10:16.360 --> 10:18.020
Speak out if you feel wronged.

10:19.240 --> 10:20.750
We'll all be here with you.

10:27.390 --> 10:28.240
Ms. Lin.

10:31.240 --> 10:32.270
I want to go...

10:32.400 --> 10:33.560
go ask her.

10:37.120 --> 10:38.650
I want to make things clear.

10:42.480 --> 10:43.240
Okay.

10:44.630 --> 10:46.240
I'll go with you.

11:15.670 --> 11:16.550
Coming.

11:21.960 --> 11:22.550
Why are you...

11:22.550 --> 11:23.030
Mom.

11:23.840 --> 11:24.970
I want to talk to you.

11:25.030 --> 11:25.600
Who is it?

11:26.870 --> 11:28.840
The delivery driver got the wrong address.

11:28.840 --> 11:29.550
Hello,

11:29.550 --> 11:30.950
I'm Fu Xinshu's teacher.

11:31.910 --> 11:32.750
I know

11:32.750 --> 11:34.720
this probably isn't
the best place to talk.

11:34.720 --> 11:38.050
We'll be waiting for you
at the café at the complex entrance.

11:44.960 --> 11:46.080
Hello.

11:48.240 --> 11:50.040
-Thank you.
-Enjoy your drinks.

11:53.840 --> 11:54.840
Don't be nervous.

11:55.840 --> 11:57.910
Just say what's on your mind
when your mom gets here.

11:57.910 --> 11:59.440
Have a proper talk with her.

12:19.730 --> 12:21.480
Mom, have a drink.

12:30.600 --> 12:31.750
You know,

12:33.250 --> 12:35.320
when I rushed out of your place earlier,

12:35.320 --> 12:36.920
I almost got hit by a car.

12:45.910 --> 12:47.550
When you and Dad divorced,

12:49.520 --> 12:51.320
you left me with Grandma.

12:53.760 --> 12:55.920
I wanted you to come see me more...

12:58.670 --> 12:59.790
so

12:59.790 --> 13:01.720
I tried my best to be well-behaved.

13:02.200 --> 13:04.630
I also studied very hard.

13:07.080 --> 13:07.840
I...

13:08.550 --> 13:10.000
I was also very careful

13:11.200 --> 13:13.240
to be nice to everyone at school.

13:13.240 --> 13:14.750
I didn't dare to get angry.

13:19.450 --> 13:20.400
I thought...

13:20.550 --> 13:22.150
I thought if I did all that...

13:22.710 --> 13:23.870
you'd come back

13:24.150 --> 13:25.200
to see me.

13:32.670 --> 13:34.440
Now I finally understand.

13:35.720 --> 13:38.180
You were only ever
interested in that money.

13:43.420 --> 13:44.660
Why?

13:52.150 --> 13:53.530
I'm deep in

13:53.840 --> 13:55.330
credit card debt.

13:56.510 --> 13:57.960
I had no other choice.

13:59.750 --> 14:00.960
My current husband

14:00.960 --> 14:02.410
looks down on me

14:02.510 --> 14:04.200
because I've been married before.

14:04.200 --> 14:06.200
I can only use money to prove myself.

14:10.510 --> 14:11.480
Mom,

14:11.480 --> 14:13.080
that's not what I was asking.

14:13.510 --> 14:14.720
Xinshu,

14:15.110 --> 14:17.030
Mom is already very tired.

14:17.240 --> 14:18.510
Right now, just keeping my life together

14:18.510 --> 14:21.100
with my current husband
takes everything I have.

14:21.100 --> 14:22.180
Fu Xinshu's mom,

14:23.120 --> 14:25.030
you really shouldn't say that.

14:31.910 --> 14:32.750
It's fine.

14:34.700 --> 14:36.780
I got the answer I came here for.

14:38.150 --> 14:39.880
That's good enough, I suppose.

14:49.440 --> 14:50.840
Mom, I've grown up.

14:52.120 --> 14:53.510
You could've told me

14:53.510 --> 14:54.960
what you were going through earlier.

14:54.960 --> 14:56.510
I would've understood.

15:03.200 --> 15:04.430
From now on,

15:05.270 --> 15:07.200
I hope you live your life well.

15:08.630 --> 15:09.440
And I...

15:09.440 --> 15:11.720
I'll live mine well too.

15:18.870 --> 15:19.630
Goodbye.

16:09.690 --> 16:11.540
We shouldn't have let Wen Chengye keep it.

16:09.840 --> 16:16.190
[Welcome]

16:13.910 --> 16:14.710
They're here.

16:15.030 --> 16:15.670
Coach is here.

16:15.670 --> 16:16.670
Yes, it's Ms. Lin.

16:17.750 --> 16:19.510
-Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

16:19.510 --> 16:21.000
-Hello, Coach.
-Hello, Coach.

16:21.000 --> 16:23.030
Ms. Lin, what happened to your hand?

16:23.890 --> 16:24.760
It's nothing.

16:24.790 --> 16:26.000
Just a little scrape.

16:26.000 --> 16:27.330
Don't worry, everyone.

16:27.480 --> 16:28.680
Fu Xinshu is fine too.

16:31.600 --> 16:32.960
Why are you all standing outside?

16:32.960 --> 16:33.670
Let's go in.

16:34.600 --> 16:36.600
It's not that we don't want to go in.

16:37.150 --> 16:38.030
Ms. Lin,

16:38.240 --> 16:39.630
it seems you've booked the hotel

16:39.630 --> 16:41.030
for tomorrow by mistake.

16:41.630 --> 16:43.870
And the university next door
is having a seminar.

16:43.870 --> 16:45.440
The nearby hotels are fully booked.

16:45.440 --> 16:47.150
We've got nowhere to stay.

16:47.890 --> 16:49.350
[Ruxing Hotel Room Reservations]

16:50.600 --> 16:52.150
I really booked the wrong date.

16:52.150 --> 16:54.810
Sounds exactly like
something Ms. Lin would do.

16:55.140 --> 16:56.270
The hotel's sorted.

16:57.030 --> 16:57.750
Let's go.

16:57.750 --> 16:59.000
That fast?

16:59.000 --> 17:00.700
Coach, you're amazing.

17:00.950 --> 17:02.270
Good thing Coach saved the day.

17:02.270 --> 17:04.000
We don't have to
sleep on the streets tonight.

17:04.000 --> 17:05.260
Where's the new hotel?

17:08.720 --> 17:10.240
Is this a palace?

17:10.880 --> 17:12.270
I've got to send this to my mom.

17:12.270 --> 17:13.869
We're in the right place, aren't we?

17:13.869 --> 17:15.240
This place is gorgeous.

17:15.240 --> 17:16.510
I heard this is one of Hengjiu's hotels.

17:16.510 --> 17:18.440
I've never stayed in a hotel this fancy.

17:18.440 --> 17:19.550
Well, now you have.

17:19.550 --> 17:21.160
And it's free.

17:21.160 --> 17:22.920
It feels like a dream.

17:26.240 --> 17:28.200
Coach, are we really staying here tonight?

17:28.200 --> 17:28.960
-For real?
-Really?

17:28.960 --> 17:30.000
We're staying here.

17:30.000 --> 17:31.830
-Thank you, Coach!
-Thank you, Coach!

17:31.830 --> 17:32.920
Don't thank me.

17:32.920 --> 17:34.070
I'm unemployed

17:34.200 --> 17:36.200
and have to pay rent to Ms. Lin.

17:36.960 --> 17:38.270
You should thank Ms. Lin.

17:38.270 --> 17:40.350
-Thank you, Ms. Lin!
-Thank you, Ms. Lin!

17:40.350 --> 17:41.030
Come on, let's go.

17:41.030 --> 17:42.400
-Thank you, Ms. Lin.
-Thank you, Ms. Lin.

17:42.400 --> 17:44.270
-Thank you, Ms. Lin.
-Thank you, Ms. Lin.

17:44.270 --> 17:44.800
Let's go.

17:45.720 --> 17:48.590
I don't think my credit card limit
is high enough for this.

17:48.590 --> 17:50.000
You can run a tab with me.

17:50.240 --> 17:50.880
Boss,

17:51.010 --> 17:52.510
let's take a picture together.

17:52.510 --> 17:53.200
Mr. Wang.

17:53.200 --> 17:54.110
Hurry up.

17:54.110 --> 17:54.680
Come on,

17:54.680 --> 17:55.400
let's take a group photo.

17:55.400 --> 17:56.700
Welcome, Mr. Wang.

17:57.110 --> 17:58.240
The eight rooms you asked for

17:58.240 --> 17:59.000
-are ready.
-Guys, guys...

17:59.000 --> 18:00.590
Two deluxe single rooms

18:00.590 --> 18:02.240
and six business twin rooms.

18:02.240 --> 18:04.270
Wen Chengye, have you finished
your counseling class?

18:04.270 --> 18:05.030
Where are you?

18:05.030 --> 18:06.000
100% genuine.

18:06.790 --> 18:08.390
You have to buy this photo.

18:08.640 --> 18:10.400
Isn't Ms. Lin paying?

18:10.880 --> 18:11.640
Come on, come on.

18:11.640 --> 18:12.640
Bring your ID cards.

18:12.640 --> 18:13.410
-Okay.
-Stop taking photos.

18:13.410 --> 18:15.240
-Okay.
-Excuse me.

18:15.240 --> 18:16.240
This way, please.

18:17.110 --> 18:17.830
-I brought it.
-You did?

18:17.830 --> 18:18.880
-What about you?
-Let's go.

18:18.880 --> 18:19.880
-Boss.
-Something came up?

18:19.880 --> 18:20.940
I'll be right back.

18:21.090 --> 18:23.310
-Help me with mine too.
-Come on, little Yu Ming.

18:23.310 --> 18:24.840
Please show me your ID card.

18:25.200 --> 18:27.070
I'm sharing a room with my boss.

18:28.340 --> 18:29.070
Who said I want to share a room with you?

18:29.070 --> 18:29.880
Ms. Lin,

18:30.680 --> 18:31.510
maybe

18:31.510 --> 18:32.840
cancel one of the rooms.

18:33.350 --> 18:34.350
I have something early tomorrow morning,

18:34.350 --> 18:36.270
so I need to
take the high-speed train back.

18:36.270 --> 18:37.130
I just checked.

18:37.640 --> 18:38.880
There are still tickets available.

18:38.880 --> 18:40.270
But it's so late.

18:40.270 --> 18:41.790
I-I'm worried.

18:42.030 --> 18:42.790
Then let me take you.

18:42.790 --> 18:43.590
I'll take him.

18:44.590 --> 18:46.110
I'll add the transportation fees
to your bill later.

18:46.110 --> 18:47.920
You've lost the chance
to share a room with me.

18:47.920 --> 18:49.310
Like I'd want to.

19:01.200 --> 19:01.830
Thanks.

19:02.350 --> 19:03.070
You stayed so late

19:03.070 --> 19:04.930
because of Fu Xinshu, didn't you?

19:07.960 --> 19:09.360
You're overthinking it.

19:11.030 --> 19:13.070
Only fools let
their families manipulate them.

19:13.070 --> 19:13.830
I came

19:14.400 --> 19:16.730
purely to watch him
make a fool of himself.

19:18.160 --> 19:19.420
Be careful on your way.

19:29.720 --> 19:30.440
Hello,

19:30.880 --> 19:32.740
Fu Xinshu's mom? This is Wang Fa.

19:32.930 --> 19:34.590
-Put it on my side.
-Put it on my side.

19:34.590 --> 19:35.590
Sichuan.

19:36.880 --> 19:38.960
-So you guys can't handle spicy food.
-Coach.

19:38.960 --> 19:40.220
Hello, Coach.

19:40.250 --> 19:41.480
Hello, Coach.

19:41.480 --> 19:42.790
I'm not too late, am I?

19:42.790 --> 19:44.350
Your timing couldn't be better.

19:44.350 --> 19:46.110
It's just done. Come on.

19:46.110 --> 19:47.200
-Thank you, Ms. Lin.
-Coach is back.

19:47.200 --> 19:48.790
Everyone, let's thank Coach!

19:48.790 --> 19:51.240
-Put the meat in!
-Thank you, Coach!

19:51.240 --> 19:53.160
The meat's finally done!

19:53.750 --> 19:54.880
Are you really okay?

19:56.590 --> 19:58.790
Honestly, I'd be lying
if I said I didn't feel bad.

19:58.790 --> 20:00.920
I won't force her to accept me anymore.

20:01.550 --> 20:03.960
Thinking about it this way,
I actually feel a lot lighter.

20:03.960 --> 20:06.560
Anyway, I don't have money
to give her anymore.

20:07.510 --> 20:08.350
It's fine.

20:09.590 --> 20:10.920
Things will get better.

20:11.310 --> 20:13.480
She doesn't come to see us,
and we don't see her.

20:13.480 --> 20:14.880
Out of sight, out of mind,

20:14.880 --> 20:15.590
right?

20:15.590 --> 20:17.270
If anything's on your mind, just tell us.

20:17.270 --> 20:19.070
-Yeah.
-You have us!

20:19.070 --> 20:20.240
We're all here for you.

20:20.240 --> 20:21.160
I'm really fine.

20:21.160 --> 20:22.560
I've thought it through.

20:22.610 --> 20:24.480
There's no point wasting time on people
who aren't worth it.

20:24.480 --> 20:25.830
That's right!

20:26.440 --> 20:27.350
Come on, come on!

20:27.350 --> 20:28.680
Ms. Lin, Coach, cheers!

20:28.680 --> 20:30.550
-Come on.
-Cheers! Cheers!

20:30.550 --> 20:32.920
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

20:33.510 --> 20:34.750
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

20:36.310 --> 20:37.310
Thank you, Coach.

20:38.750 --> 20:40.750
Take care of yourselves from now on.

20:42.930 --> 20:44.020
This one's done.

20:45.750 --> 20:46.590
W-What's this?

20:46.590 --> 20:47.880
Is this a volcano?

20:47.880 --> 20:48.960
-Is it Volcano Beef?
-No!

20:48.960 --> 20:49.790
How come you have this dish?

20:49.790 --> 20:51.000
I want some too!

20:51.190 --> 20:52.190
Don't grab!

20:53.350 --> 20:54.400
Come over and eat with us!

20:54.400 --> 20:55.240
Ms. Lin, Coach!

20:55.240 --> 20:56.590
We're not buddies right now.

20:56.590 --> 20:57.070
What?

20:57.880 --> 20:58.880
Let me see.

20:59.000 --> 20:59.610
I'm not eating the spicy dish.

20:59.610 --> 21:01.500
-It's not done yet.
-Hold on.

21:02.830 --> 21:03.750
Both tables have this dish.

21:03.750 --> 21:05.410
Order more if it's not enough.

21:06.570 --> 21:07.930
-Coach, look.
-Meat.

21:08.510 --> 21:09.570
You guys eat first.

21:25.520 --> 21:26.520
Coach,

21:26.550 --> 21:27.830
the vibe is so good.

21:27.830 --> 21:29.960
You sure you won't have a drink with me?

21:30.440 --> 21:32.370
Alcohol isn't good for your wound.

21:40.200 --> 21:41.060
Safflower oil?

21:41.400 --> 21:42.510
Bought it on the way.

21:42.510 --> 21:43.720
It's good for bruises.

21:43.720 --> 21:44.750
No need.

21:44.750 --> 21:46.010
I don't like the smell.

21:48.680 --> 21:51.310
It can offset the hotel fees
I fronted today.

22:13.240 --> 22:14.680
Be a little gentler.

22:15.400 --> 22:15.960
Okay.

22:21.310 --> 22:22.970
Look how sweet they are.

22:23.030 --> 22:24.750
They're clearly in the honeymoon phase.

22:24.750 --> 22:25.880
He's just putting medicated oil on me.

22:25.880 --> 22:27.070
Don't misunderstand.

22:27.070 --> 22:27.750
Sorry about that.

22:27.460 --> 22:32.600
♪ With the evening breeze
whispering in my ear ♪

22:33.610 --> 22:38.950
♪ Fireworks bloom across the sky ♪

22:39.830 --> 22:41.790
♪ Shimmering in your eyes ♪

22:40.720 --> 22:42.330
To save Fu Xinshu,

22:42.360 --> 22:43.850
you actually ran out to stop a car?

22:42.790 --> 22:48.330
♪ And spreading into
a gentle sea of stars ♪

22:44.240 --> 22:46.070
May I ask what you were thinking?

22:49.740 --> 22:50.540
I don't know.

22:52.030 --> 22:54.960
I wasn't really thinking about anything
at the time.

22:56.160 --> 22:56.960
I understand.

23:01.310 --> 23:02.350
Understand what?

23:05.240 --> 23:06.550
I too once had a student

23:06.550 --> 23:08.240
I would do anything for.

23:10.250 --> 23:12.360
[Three years ago; London, England]

23:11.000 --> 23:11.880
Go! Go!

23:11.880 --> 23:13.480
Let's go! Go get it!

23:13.480 --> 23:14.350
Come on!

23:16.720 --> 23:18.180
Run forward! Run forward!

23:24.950 --> 23:25.830
Nice shot! Nice shot!

23:25.830 --> 23:26.480
Nice shot!

23:42.550 --> 23:43.770
Are you Winfred?

23:44.030 --> 23:45.070
I know you.

23:49.200 --> 23:50.800
Can you give me an autograph?

23:51.350 --> 23:52.720
I'll definitely work hard

23:52.720 --> 23:53.920
and make it to Nanton.

24:02.390 --> 24:03.650
I'll give you a chance.

24:03.720 --> 24:04.580
How about that?

24:06.760 --> 24:08.940
[Winfred Wang]

24:12.340 --> 24:14.920
[Nanton]

24:20.550 --> 24:23.000
[Defensive Strategies]

24:27.270 --> 24:28.030
Hello?

24:28.310 --> 24:29.310
Where are you?

24:29.920 --> 24:31.240
Well, the board meeting starts
in 10 minutes.

24:31.240 --> 24:32.400
You can't be late.

24:32.640 --> 24:33.750
I know.

24:33.750 --> 24:34.880
Oh, one more thing.

24:34.880 --> 24:36.880
Are you sure you want to start Jason?

24:36.920 --> 24:37.790
He's only been here for four months.

24:37.790 --> 24:38.550
Aren't you worried

24:38.550 --> 24:40.590
that those old guys
will fire you over this?

24:40.590 --> 24:41.400
Don't worry.

24:41.680 --> 24:43.510
I can handle those old fogeys.

24:48.550 --> 24:49.270
Well done.

24:49.750 --> 24:50.830
Coach!

24:53.200 --> 24:54.590
Coach, I just scored!

24:54.590 --> 24:56.790
I scored two! Two!

24:56.790 --> 24:58.940
I dribbled past them so easily!

24:59.000 --> 25:02.590
Coach, I'll definitely score more goals
in the future.

25:15.200 --> 25:16.830
This is the first time

25:17.480 --> 25:19.510
you've told me your story.

25:21.790 --> 25:22.680
Coach,

25:23.240 --> 25:25.720
what made you start trusting me?

25:26.640 --> 25:28.100
Did I not trust you before?

25:29.510 --> 25:31.480
I may have dropped out of
my Ph.D. program,

25:31.480 --> 25:32.750
but I'm pretty solid

25:32.750 --> 25:34.070
in psychology.

25:36.200 --> 25:37.310
That's because today is

25:37.310 --> 25:39.840
also the first time
I've seen this side of you.

25:42.680 --> 25:44.030
So it's fair.

25:51.310 --> 25:53.550
Maybe we should talk about something else.

25:51.530 --> 25:53.580
♪ I caught your eyes ♪

25:54.070 --> 25:56.440
♪ On the summer night ♪

25:56.930 --> 26:02.440
♪ A star that glows so bright ♪

25:59.790 --> 26:02.000
If we're going to talk about the match,

26:02.000 --> 26:03.960
we'd need to review the match footage.

26:03.960 --> 26:06.220
♪ A spark in my heart ♪

26:04.550 --> 26:06.790
Talking about
theoretical knowledge outdoors seems...

26:06.790 --> 26:08.480
No work talk.

26:06.920 --> 26:12.710
♪ Disappear in my dream, secretly ♪

26:08.480 --> 26:09.920
Then what should we talk about?

26:09.920 --> 26:10.830
You start.

26:11.000 --> 26:12.260
I'll follow your lead.

26:16.100 --> 26:21.350
♪ With the evening breeze
whispering in my ear ♪

26:19.110 --> 26:20.790
Has anyone ever told you

26:20.790 --> 26:22.790
that you have very beautiful eyes?

26:22.250 --> 26:27.720
♪ Fireworks bloom across the sky ♪

26:24.920 --> 26:28.050
You just need a mind map
to straighten out your behavior.

26:28.470 --> 26:30.990
♪ Shimmering in your eyes ♪

26:29.510 --> 26:31.140
Then has anyone ever told you

26:31.430 --> 26:33.580
that when you're not making me
scan a QR code to pay you,

26:31.430 --> 26:37.250
♪ And spreading into
a gentle sea of stars ♪

26:33.790 --> 26:35.790
you're actually pretty handsome?

26:35.790 --> 26:36.960
I won't split the hotpot bill

26:36.960 --> 26:37.960
with you today.

26:40.500 --> 26:42.470
♪ Every night ♪

26:41.240 --> 26:42.310
Then has anyone ever told you

26:42.310 --> 26:45.000
that when you're not talking,
you have a certain mysterious,

26:43.250 --> 26:45.370
♪ I reach for starlight ♪

26:45.000 --> 26:46.510
melancholic aura?

26:46.120 --> 26:48.150
♪ Wandering through dreams with you ♪

26:48.520 --> 26:49.450
♪ I follow ♪

26:48.550 --> 26:49.680
-And has anyone ever...
-Ms. Lin!

26:49.680 --> 26:50.480
Coach!

26:50.480 --> 26:52.350
Fu Xinshu's mom just called him,

26:52.350 --> 26:53.950
and she even transferred...

26:55.160 --> 26:56.510
the money back.

26:59.270 --> 27:00.000
Alright, Qin.

27:00.000 --> 27:02.000
Let's talk about it when we get back.

27:02.350 --> 27:03.580
Ms. Lin,

27:04.070 --> 27:04.880
Coach,

27:05.550 --> 27:07.030
what are you doing?

27:07.920 --> 27:08.920
Rubbing some medicated oil on me.

27:08.920 --> 27:09.960
Can't you see?

27:15.830 --> 27:17.430
Aren't you going to explain?

27:18.640 --> 27:19.850
Explain what?

27:21.200 --> 27:23.460
A clear conscience fears no accusation.

27:26.060 --> 27:27.470
Fair enough.

27:30.550 --> 27:31.750
I don't buy it though.

27:46.750 --> 27:48.790
You called Fu Xinshu's mom?

27:51.920 --> 27:53.880
I think she still loves Fu Xinshu.

27:56.000 --> 27:57.280
I have to admit,

27:57.450 --> 27:58.980
you really are thoughtful.

28:05.790 --> 28:08.590
You said before
that you wouldn't be staying long.

28:08.720 --> 28:09.920
What do you think now?

28:11.160 --> 28:12.620
Whether I stay long or not,

28:13.030 --> 28:15.430
I won't let anyone under my care
be wronged.

28:17.070 --> 28:18.960
That domineering,
"alpha male" one-liner...

28:18.960 --> 28:21.920
I must say, even I was grossed out.

28:23.920 --> 28:25.780
Then I'll tone it down from now on.

28:28.220 --> 28:28.850
Oh,

28:29.000 --> 28:30.860
what kind of car was it that hit us?

28:32.450 --> 28:33.290
Why?

28:34.160 --> 28:35.760
Its brakes were pretty good.

28:36.960 --> 28:38.550
Ms. Lin, you always focus on

28:39.070 --> 28:40.640
the most unexpected things.

28:40.640 --> 28:41.960
You just noticed?

29:00.880 --> 29:01.750
Tell us,

29:01.750 --> 29:02.460
Mr. Zhang.

29:03.440 --> 29:04.200
Ms. Wang,

29:04.750 --> 29:07.400
we've found a breakthrough
for our photovoltaic products.

29:07.400 --> 29:09.960
We're getting positive feedback
in the African market.

29:09.960 --> 29:12.560
Just give me
next quarter's projected growth.

29:12.790 --> 29:14.920
Our projected growth next quarter...

29:16.200 --> 29:19.060
is expected to be 5% points lower
than this quarter.

29:20.750 --> 29:22.640
If we keep operating at a loss,

29:22.640 --> 29:27.040
we'll have to seriously reconsider
our investment in the photovoltaic plant.

29:27.270 --> 29:28.400
Anyone else?

29:33.240 --> 29:34.030
Ms. Wang.

29:40.160 --> 29:41.640
Is the club still printing out

29:41.640 --> 29:43.040
budget sheets like this?

29:43.480 --> 29:45.070
We need to move forward
with office automation.

29:45.070 --> 29:45.880
Understood.

29:57.790 --> 29:59.240
I'm optimistic
about Hengjiu Youth Academy,

29:59.240 --> 30:01.720
and I believe you can
achieve even better results.

30:01.720 --> 30:02.680
Thank you, Ms. Wang.

30:02.680 --> 30:04.000
We won't let you down.

30:05.110 --> 30:05.880
By the way,

30:05.880 --> 30:08.310
I heard
the youth academy coach is retiring.

30:08.310 --> 30:09.160
Yes.

30:09.160 --> 30:10.720
We were just discussing it yesterday.

30:10.720 --> 30:11.750
The club has decided

30:11.750 --> 30:13.680
to recruit a top coach from overseas

30:13.680 --> 30:14.720
to bring fresh ideas and energy

30:14.720 --> 30:16.550
to the youth academy program.

30:17.200 --> 30:18.310
Do you have someone in mind?

30:18.310 --> 30:19.790
We do. A very promising one.

30:19.790 --> 30:21.310
He just returned from the UK.

30:21.310 --> 30:22.720
We've decided to poach him.

30:22.720 --> 30:23.680
Tell me more.

30:24.550 --> 30:25.570
He's of Asian descent,

30:25.570 --> 30:27.200
and his English name is Winfred.

30:27.200 --> 30:28.440
Because of his outstanding record,

30:28.440 --> 30:30.350
everyone calls him "Mr. Win."

30:31.160 --> 30:32.720
However, he's very mysterious,

30:32.720 --> 30:34.450
always impossible to pin down.

30:36.160 --> 30:39.030
I'm very interested in this man, Mr. Win.

30:39.750 --> 30:41.030
Move quickly on this.

30:41.030 --> 30:43.030
You can increase the budget if necessary.

30:43.030 --> 30:43.760
Understood.

30:45.710 --> 30:54.220
[Hongjing No. 8 High School Football Team
Crushes Lyujing International]

30:46.070 --> 30:47.200
Look at my masterpiece.

30:47.200 --> 30:48.790
Doesn't it look absolutely epic?

30:48.790 --> 30:50.070
Why do I feel like

30:50.070 --> 30:51.310
it's hanging a little crooked on the left?

30:51.310 --> 30:52.350
No, it's not.

30:52.350 --> 30:53.110
You need glasses now.

30:53.110 --> 30:54.750
You know,

30:54.750 --> 30:56.400
now that it's up there,
it really looks imposing.

30:56.400 --> 30:58.310
Are we being a bit too flashy?

30:58.790 --> 31:00.510
Let's take it down in a few days.

31:00.510 --> 31:01.790
It needs to stay up for at least a week.

31:01.790 --> 31:03.680
-Yeah.
-Zheng.

31:03.680 --> 31:04.680
Come on, come on.

31:04.210 --> 31:07.400
[Hongjing No. 8 High School Football Team
Crushes Lyujing International]

31:04.680 --> 31:05.750
Take a picture for me.

31:05.750 --> 31:07.070
I've got to send it to my dad

31:07.070 --> 31:08.550
so he stops saying I don't study hard.

31:08.550 --> 31:09.310
-Come on, come on.
-Show-off.

31:09.310 --> 31:11.240
-That pose is terrible.
-Way too ugly.

31:11.240 --> 31:12.790
It's too ugly. Let me teach you.

31:12.790 --> 31:14.790
Too bad today's not
parent-teacher conference day.

31:14.790 --> 31:16.720
I'd show my mom this.

31:17.750 --> 31:19.110
Excuse me, excuse me.

31:18.000 --> 31:19.810
[Hongjing No. 8 High School Football Team
Crushes Lyujing International]

31:20.510 --> 31:21.590
What do these words say?

31:21.590 --> 31:22.920
Can you read them for me?

31:23.200 --> 31:24.240
Um...

31:27.550 --> 31:28.030
Hey.

31:29.270 --> 31:29.880
Hey!

31:30.240 --> 31:31.750
I didn't even get her name.

31:31.750 --> 31:32.680
We don't have much dignity left.

31:32.680 --> 31:34.030
Can you stop embarrassing us?

31:34.030 --> 31:35.750
So what?

31:35.750 --> 31:37.010
I'm bringing us honor.

31:38.000 --> 31:38.550
Qin!

31:38.960 --> 31:39.400
Come here.

31:39.400 --> 31:41.000
Let's take a group photo together.

31:41.000 --> 31:42.400
-Right, right.
-Come on!

31:42.420 --> 31:44.150
-Come on.
-Let's take a photo.

31:45.960 --> 31:47.000
Stand close to me.

31:47.000 --> 31:48.000
Whose hand is this?

31:48.000 --> 31:48.880
Smile!

31:48.880 --> 31:51.440
Come on, three, two, one!

31:51.440 --> 31:54.640
Cheese!

31:57.160 --> 31:57.910
Snap it!

31:57.930 --> 31:59.240
-Snap it!
-Come on.

31:59.240 --> 32:00.240
Hello, Director.

32:04.030 --> 32:05.030
-Director! Director!
-Hello, Director!

32:05.030 --> 32:06.350
Go ahead and take it.
Why are you hiding it?

32:06.350 --> 32:08.200
-We're not hiding anything.
-Nothing.

32:08.200 --> 32:09.790
Director, you said

32:09.790 --> 32:10.680
phones weren't allowed at school,

32:10.680 --> 32:12.110
but you didn't say c
ameras weren't allowed, right?

32:12.110 --> 32:13.840
Did I say they weren't allowed?

32:17.590 --> 32:21.240
Our football team completely defeated
Lyujing International.

32:21.680 --> 32:23.350
You won the match this time,

32:23.350 --> 32:25.200
and the school is genuinely proud of you.

32:25.200 --> 32:26.200
It's okay to show off

32:26.200 --> 32:26.930
a little bit!

32:31.070 --> 32:33.600
-Thank you, Director!
-Thank you, Director!

32:33.830 --> 32:34.590
Since the Director is here,

32:34.590 --> 32:35.750
let's take a group photo later

32:35.750 --> 32:36.830
and put it on the wall of honor!

32:36.830 --> 32:37.550
Sure!

32:37.550 --> 32:38.790
Come on, come on.

32:38.790 --> 32:40.390
Wall of honor! Wall of honor!

32:40.720 --> 32:41.790
Director, come on.

32:41.790 --> 32:43.960
-Come on.
-Three, two, one.

32:43.960 --> 32:46.590
Cheese!

32:46.590 --> 32:48.070
Ms. Lin!

32:48.070 --> 32:49.720
Check out the photos we took.

32:51.880 --> 32:53.200
Quick!

32:53.200 --> 32:54.200
Print this photo

32:54.200 --> 32:55.350
and put it on the wall of honor.

32:55.350 --> 32:56.000
Absolutely perfect.

32:56.000 --> 32:56.790
Especially my handsome face.

32:56.790 --> 32:58.030
Come on.

32:58.030 --> 32:58.880
You really think Ms. Lin

32:58.880 --> 33:00.310
wants to stare at your face every day?

33:00.310 --> 33:01.830
She'll start having nightmares
during her lunch break naps.

33:01.830 --> 33:03.310
I'll punch you.

33:03.310 --> 33:05.640
You guys are seriously full of yourselves.

33:05.640 --> 33:07.550
Look how composed Fu is.

33:08.550 --> 33:11.000
-Fu...
-Fu is so composed.

33:11.000 --> 33:13.400
This is the result
of everyone's hard work.

33:14.350 --> 33:14.960
You know,

33:14.960 --> 33:15.890
I'm a little shy.

33:17.200 --> 33:18.000
So dramatic.

33:22.680 --> 33:23.510
Ms. Lin,

33:23.510 --> 33:24.960
the parents of these students are here.

33:24.960 --> 33:26.160
Come with me quickly.

33:27.960 --> 33:28.790
What's going on?

33:28.790 --> 33:29.400
I don't know either,

33:29.400 --> 33:30.790
but it seems really urgent.

33:30.790 --> 33:31.590
What should we do?

33:31.590 --> 33:32.550
Don't worry. I'll go take a look.

33:32.550 --> 33:34.400
-Well...
-Wait.

33:37.000 --> 33:38.750
My mom is so busy with work.

33:38.770 --> 33:40.000
She probably won't come.

33:40.000 --> 33:41.960
Did my dad come too?

33:43.550 --> 33:45.000
My dad definitely wouldn't bother.

33:45.000 --> 33:45.920
Director,

33:45.920 --> 33:48.400
our Chen Jianghe is
already in his senior year.

33:48.400 --> 33:51.060
He shouldn't
keep wasting his time on football.

33:51.350 --> 33:53.510
The team isn't going anywhere.

33:53.510 --> 33:55.270
Isn't this just fooling around?

33:55.270 --> 33:56.240
Isn't this a waste of time?

33:56.240 --> 33:58.310
-It's a waste of time.
-Listen to me.

33:58.750 --> 33:59.400
As parents ourselves,

33:59.400 --> 34:01.640
we understand your concerns.

34:01.880 --> 34:03.510
But you must trust the school.

34:03.510 --> 34:05.270
We'll handle this properly.

34:05.270 --> 34:06.960
But the college entrance exam is
coming soon.

34:06.960 --> 34:08.960
There's no time!

34:09.710 --> 34:11.510
This is our team supervisor, Ms. Lin.

34:11.510 --> 34:12.440
Come on, Ms. Lin.

34:13.550 --> 34:14.630
I believe Ms. Lin

34:14.630 --> 34:17.630
will definitely give you
a satisfactory explanation.

34:17.630 --> 34:18.590
Hello, parents.

34:18.590 --> 34:19.630
I'm Lin Wanxing.

34:20.000 --> 34:21.360
You're Ms. Lin, right?

34:21.630 --> 34:24.110
Our Lu went home limping yesterday.

34:24.110 --> 34:25.770
I pressed him on it right away,

34:25.880 --> 34:26.710
and that's when he finally said

34:26.710 --> 34:28.440
that he got injured
during yesterday's football match.

34:28.440 --> 34:30.639
I immediately took him to the hospital.

34:30.800 --> 34:32.110
Playing football

34:32.110 --> 34:34.510
is already affecting
the children's health.

34:34.510 --> 34:35.360
I want to know—

34:35.360 --> 34:37.090
how do you plan to explain this?

34:37.800 --> 34:39.030
What did the doctor say?

34:39.030 --> 34:41.150
The X-rays showed the bones were fine,

34:41.150 --> 34:42.750
but he has a ligament strain.

34:43.280 --> 34:45.510
They're already in their senior year.

34:45.510 --> 34:46.550
Yet the school...

34:46.550 --> 34:46.960
Isn't this

34:46.960 --> 34:48.590
just taking advantage of our kids?

34:48.590 --> 34:49.400
Exactly.

34:49.400 --> 34:51.030
-Yeah.
-Taking advantage?

34:51.030 --> 34:51.630
Just because

34:51.630 --> 34:52.920
our children's grades

34:52.920 --> 34:54.070
aren't great,

34:54.070 --> 34:55.710
you make them play football.

34:55.710 --> 34:57.710
Why don't you send the class officers
to do this kind of thing?

34:57.710 --> 34:58.630
Exactly.

34:58.630 --> 34:59.590
What are the class officers doing?

34:59.590 --> 35:00.800
-Yeah.
-Why aren't they playing?

35:00.800 --> 35:01.320
Parents.

35:01.320 --> 35:02.000
Parents.

35:02.000 --> 35:03.070
We

35:03.070 --> 35:04.600
understand your concerns.

35:05.070 --> 35:05.930
Director Qian,

35:06.590 --> 35:08.850
why don't we report this to the principal

35:09.230 --> 35:11.840
and stop organizing football matches
for the kids anymore?

35:11.840 --> 35:13.110
-Right.
-That's right.

35:13.110 --> 35:15.030
They should just focus on studying.

35:15.030 --> 35:15.840
But...

35:16.360 --> 35:18.230
they fought so hard

35:18.230 --> 35:19.960
to earn a spot in the next match.

35:20.480 --> 35:22.150
We can't just give that up.

35:22.150 --> 35:24.360
Even the Director said no more football.

35:24.360 --> 35:26.920
-Ms. Lin, maybe say a little less.
-Aren't their grades more important?

35:26.920 --> 35:28.320
How will they get into college?

35:28.320 --> 35:29.150
There's no time left.

35:29.150 --> 35:30.590
You all believe

35:30.590 --> 35:33.300
that football will affect their grades?

35:33.510 --> 35:34.760
But as far as I know,

35:34.760 --> 35:36.800
they still trained
during the first semester of Grade 10

35:36.800 --> 35:38.860
and not at all in the second semester.

35:40.400 --> 35:41.190
So?

35:43.150 --> 35:45.070
Mr. Wang, could you pull up

35:45.070 --> 35:47.000
their average grade rankings

35:47.000 --> 35:48.930
for major exams in Grades 10 and 11?

35:49.070 --> 35:50.000
Everyone, come take a look.

35:50.000 --> 35:51.020
Let's go.

35:54.220 --> 35:55.490
[Student Grade Records; Class 8]

35:56.530 --> 35:59.300
[Zhi Hui]

35:59.800 --> 36:01.030
Let's compare

36:01.030 --> 36:03.360
their rankings across the two semesters.

36:15.480 --> 36:18.020
What can
these two columns of rankings prove?

36:17.660 --> 36:19.910
[No Smoking]

36:18.360 --> 36:19.510
Exactly.

36:19.630 --> 36:20.670
These two columns...

36:20.670 --> 36:22.710
Our Qi Liang's ranking barely changed.

36:21.800 --> 36:24.720
[Fu Xinshu] [Qi Liang]

36:22.960 --> 36:23.710
But Fu Xinshu

36:23.710 --> 36:26.110
actually improved in the second semester.

36:26.190 --> 36:27.190
What about Qin Ao?

36:27.800 --> 36:29.440
He went from 678th

36:29.460 --> 36:30.980
to 690th.

36:31.510 --> 36:33.800
His ranking still dropped
even when he wasn't playing football.

36:33.800 --> 36:34.510
One data point

36:34.510 --> 36:36.000
doesn't tell us much, right?

36:36.000 --> 36:37.480
Exactly.

36:37.480 --> 36:39.320
We can use statistical analysis

36:39.320 --> 36:40.580
to reach a conclusion.

36:42.880 --> 36:44.080
And the conclusion is

36:44.110 --> 36:44.800
that these students' rankings

36:44.800 --> 36:46.320
across the two semesters

36:46.270 --> 36:47.540
[Name] [Chen Jianghe]
[Qin Ao] [Zheng Feiyang]

36:46.320 --> 36:48.960
show no statistically
significant difference.

36:48.960 --> 36:50.110
What does that mean?

36:50.480 --> 36:51.630
It means

36:51.880 --> 36:52.880
playing football

36:53.110 --> 36:56.040
likely does not affect
their academic performance.

36:56.440 --> 36:58.400
Aren't you just trying to say
that our kids have poor grades,

36:58.400 --> 36:59.880
and it doesn't matter
whether they play football or not?

36:59.880 --> 37:02.190
-Why beat around the bush?
-That's not what I mean.

37:01.840 --> 37:03.710
[No Smoking]

37:02.190 --> 37:03.630
Then what did you mean?

37:03.630 --> 37:04.400
You just look down on

37:04.400 --> 37:06.150
our kids with poor grades, don't you?

37:06.150 --> 37:07.230
No, no.

37:07.230 --> 37:08.480
I know our kids

37:08.480 --> 37:10.590
have always loved football.

37:10.590 --> 37:12.440
But they're in their senior year now,

37:12.440 --> 37:14.640
the most important year of their lives.

37:14.920 --> 37:16.190
As parents,

37:16.190 --> 37:16.960
we just want them

37:16.960 --> 37:18.760
to get into a decent university

37:18.760 --> 37:19.920
and study hard

37:20.150 --> 37:22.150
so they can have a stable future
ahead of them.

37:22.150 --> 37:23.360
Are we wrong for that?

37:23.360 --> 37:24.480
Exactly.

37:25.000 --> 37:27.000
Does getting into a good university

37:27.150 --> 37:28.480
really guarantee a stable future?

37:28.480 --> 37:28.960
What...

37:28.960 --> 37:30.280
What kind of question is that?

37:30.280 --> 37:31.670
-Of course it does!
-How could it not?

37:31.670 --> 37:32.800
Of course it does.

37:32.800 --> 37:33.760
Isn't that why you became
teachers yourselves—

37:33.760 --> 37:35.320
because you got into good universities

37:35.320 --> 37:37.000
and secured stable jobs in schools?

37:37.000 --> 37:38.110
The most important thing for them now

37:38.110 --> 37:40.240
-is to get into college.
-You've never been a struggling student.

37:40.240 --> 37:40.800
-Ms. Lin.
-So what do you know?

37:40.800 --> 37:43.030
You don't understand
those kids' situations,

37:43.030 --> 37:44.440
so say a little less.

37:45.710 --> 37:47.190
I'm not trying to argue.

37:47.400 --> 37:48.670
I'm just not sure.

37:52.630 --> 37:54.440
Sometimes a path only gets narrower

37:54.440 --> 37:56.040
the further you walk down it.

37:57.710 --> 37:58.590
Ms. Lin,

37:59.150 --> 38:01.610
I understand your educational philosophy,

38:01.630 --> 38:04.070
but we also need to be considerate
of the parents' anxiety.

38:04.070 --> 38:05.030
Exactly.

38:05.030 --> 38:06.480
-Grades matter.
-Director is right.

38:06.480 --> 38:07.710
-The old saying still holds.
-What else is there for them then?

38:07.710 --> 38:09.840
-Education can change your future.
-That's right.

38:09.840 --> 38:10.760
Playing less football

38:10.760 --> 38:11.960
and scoring even one point higher—
that's a good thing.

38:11.960 --> 38:13.590
And football isn't likely to
lead anywhere anyway.

38:13.590 --> 38:14.440
Better to just stop.

38:14.440 --> 38:15.880
What if I can get all of them

38:15.880 --> 38:18.940
into the top 500 in their grade
by the next monthly exam?

38:19.000 --> 38:19.840
-Really?
-You're kidding, right?

38:19.840 --> 38:22.570
-Yeah. Is that even possible?
-Is that possible?

38:22.590 --> 38:24.280
Can you really help them
get into the top 500?

38:24.280 --> 38:25.590
You're so young,

38:25.590 --> 38:27.000
yet you sure talk big.

38:27.000 --> 38:27.760
Exactly.

38:27.760 --> 38:28.760
You can look up our province's

38:28.760 --> 38:30.880
college entrance exam news
from seven years ago.

38:30.880 --> 38:32.070
I was

38:32.070 --> 38:33.960
the liberal arts top scorer that year.

38:33.960 --> 38:35.480
-Check it.
-Search it.

38:35.480 --> 38:36.740
-Let's see.
-This one?

38:36.760 --> 38:38.150
Six hundred seventy points.

38:37.850 --> 38:38.530
[Provincial Liberal Arts Top Scorer]

38:38.150 --> 38:39.800
I-Isn't there a photo?

38:38.550 --> 38:39.380
[Lin Wanxing
of Yongchuan Experimental High School]

38:40.440 --> 38:41.440
This really is her.

38:41.440 --> 38:42.110
It's her.

38:42.110 --> 38:44.590
Being good at studying
doesn't mean you're good at teaching.

38:44.590 --> 38:46.190
Even if you're the top scorer
on the college entrance exam,

38:46.190 --> 38:46.800
can you guarantee

38:46.800 --> 38:48.110
our children's grades will improve?

38:48.110 --> 38:49.400
-Exactly.
-That's right.

38:49.400 --> 38:50.920
Anyone can make big promises.

38:50.920 --> 38:51.670
Besides,

38:51.670 --> 38:52.590
what can one semester's grades

38:52.590 --> 38:53.800
prove anyway?

38:53.800 --> 38:55.110
-Exactly.
-The college entrance exam is coming.

38:55.110 --> 38:56.410
That's what determines their future.

38:56.410 --> 38:57.710
No matter what you say,

38:57.710 --> 39:00.190
our Feng Suo is done with football.

39:00.190 --> 39:02.030
-Lin Lu's quitting too.
-All this talk,

39:02.030 --> 39:03.030
we might as well have them
quit the team right now.

39:03.030 --> 39:03.760
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

39:03.760 --> 39:04.590
-They're quitting the team.
-Yeah.

39:04.590 --> 39:07.390
I can help them
get into their ideal universities.

39:07.670 --> 39:09.000
I'll do everything I can

39:09.280 --> 39:11.150
to help them keep playing football
without falling behind

39:11.150 --> 39:12.080
in their studies

39:12.590 --> 39:13.940
and get them

39:13.970 --> 39:15.900
into good universities together.

39:19.400 --> 39:21.260
-Should we believe her?
-Well...

39:21.400 --> 39:22.550
Ms. Lin, right?

39:23.280 --> 39:24.590
We all heard you.

39:24.590 --> 39:26.720
And all these teachers are witnesses.

39:26.760 --> 39:28.110
You'd better not back out later!

39:28.110 --> 39:29.150
Ms. Lin,

39:29.400 --> 39:30.710
if you can pull it off,

39:30.710 --> 39:32.550
our Chen Jianghe will stay on the team.

39:32.550 --> 39:33.760
But if you can't,

39:34.000 --> 39:35.510
the team has to be disbanded!

39:35.510 --> 39:36.280
Disbanded.

39:41.550 --> 39:43.550
Top 500 in the grade?

39:43.550 --> 39:44.880
A certain top scorer
in the college entrance exam just promised

39:44.880 --> 39:47.760
to get every one of us into the top 500.

39:48.400 --> 39:49.920
Ms. Lin, you are doomed.

39:49.920 --> 39:51.960
We can't possibly
make it into the top 500.

39:51.960 --> 39:54.070
That's simply impossible!

39:54.070 --> 39:55.670
Top 500!

39:55.670 --> 39:56.870
What should we do now?

39:57.280 --> 39:58.360
Alright, alright.

39:59.220 --> 40:01.420
Let's hear what Ms. Lin has to say first.

40:09.070 --> 40:10.670
Say something.

40:10.670 --> 40:11.920
You started this mess.

40:11.920 --> 40:13.480
Now fix it.

40:13.480 --> 40:14.230
-Say something.
-Yeah, say something.

40:14.230 --> 40:14.780
Yeah.

40:14.810 --> 40:16.510
-What should we do?
-Say something, Ms. Lin.

40:16.510 --> 40:17.550
Ms. Lin,

40:18.400 --> 40:20.400
if we don't make it,

40:21.280 --> 40:23.360
does that mean we can't play anymore?

40:25.070 --> 40:25.920
Why?

40:25.920 --> 40:26.960
Why bet on this?

40:26.960 --> 40:27.960
Why would you stake it on our grades?

40:27.960 --> 40:29.630
-Betting on grades?
-Why?

40:29.630 --> 40:31.510
Why did you have to bet on this?

40:32.230 --> 40:34.320
I don't know either.

40:34.320 --> 40:35.630
What should we do? What should we do?

40:35.630 --> 40:37.510
What should we do, Ms. Lin?

40:37.510 --> 40:39.280
You'd have better odds betting
that all of my wild corner kicks

40:39.280 --> 40:41.010
and wayward free kicks
would somehow end up in the net!

40:41.010 --> 40:42.760
Don't ask me.

40:42.880 --> 40:45.440
It's too late to regret it now.

41:14.690 --> 41:15.670
[Someone is following me.
Do you think he might be a flasher?]

41:15.690 --> 41:17.420
[If I just act completely unfazed,]

41:17.460 --> 41:19.980
[would it shock him greatly?]

42:15.660 --> 42:16.980
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

42:18.070 --> 42:19.560
♪ Because you're with me ♪

42:22.310 --> 42:23.750
♪ The light shimmers ♪
